50:29.110 --> 50:31.444
RAYFORD:
You wanna go someplace
in particular?

50:31.612 --> 50:34.864
No. Down,
I would prefer to go down.

50:35.032 --> 50:38.410
RAYFORD:
Now, just relax, Arthur.
Just relax and enjoy it.

50:38.577 --> 50:41.955
